summary: Changed the hood for thalmor robes to look like a Cowl instead(working Progress)
descriptionHtml:
4/8/12: Happy Easter as a gift to all you Mod junkies out there i Made the Collar Standalone on some nice Robes that Drop of Rulindil (boss at the end of Diplomatic immunity) Enjoy and Please Dont Forget To endorse, i really love seeing that you guys like it makes the work worth it -thanks!


4/5/2012: WORKING!!!! so many attempts and a few hand fulls of hair pulled out of my head its finally working (ironic...i lose hair my character gains hair) so enjoy and endorse



so basicly i took the top half of the hood and removed it so when you where hooded thalmor armor it has this super evil witch looking cowl instead of a hood. enjoy

Bugs: The Gloss maps seem a little odd.
author: longnose
